title: Trouble setting up Pixel 3 XL
content: When setting up my Pixel 3 XL, as it was connected via cable to my old Pixel, the old phone lost power, so so setup was interrupted. I now cannot finish setup. I have some apps, but no texts were transferred. How do I finish setup? The answers on this site tell me that a "finish setup" will appear in the settings, but it doesn't. How do I finish transferring all my texts, as well as anything else that wasn't transferred?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3 XL
